{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"date: 2016-05-14T10:45:40-05:00"}],"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"You cannot adjust for your bias because it is a fundamental part of how you understand the world. It is at a lower level than your senses and changes what you see, smell, and feel.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"While you can’t adjust for your bias, you can alter it over time by exposing yourself to other points of view."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow","doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow\/Archive","doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow\/2016"]]},"topicSectionsStyle":"detailedGrid","variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/brunow\/05-14-adjusting-for-your-bias"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow\/05-14-adjusting-for-your-bias","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"kind":"article","metadata":{"title":"Adjusting For Your Bias","color":{"standardColorIdentifier":"purple"},"platforms":[{"introducedAt":"2017.01.20","name":"Brunow"}],"modules":[{"name":"Brunow"}]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"references":{"doc://Brunow/documentation/Brunow/2016":{"abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow\/2016","title":"2016","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/brunow\/2016","role":"collectionGroup","kind":"article"},"doc://Brunow/documentation/Brunow":{"role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/brunow","identifier":"doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow","title":"Brunow","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"David Brunow, known as Brunow [ˈbɹunoʊ] to the folks he works with, is a human living on Earth. You might have something in common with him — if you think it is ridiculous that he is talking about himself in the first person here, so does he.","type":"text"}]},"doc://Brunow/documentation/Brunow/Arc